text: ( Source : City of Guelph ) All invited to attend free event October 8 GUELPH, ON, October 2, 2015 - The public is invited to join Mayor Cam Guthrie for a free event to mark World Mental Health Day , to be held October 8 at 11:30 a.m. at Guelph
